summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to and amending plat 221E, page 8, of the Official Zoning Map of The City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Tracts 8 through 11 of Kennedy Acre Tracts from RS 7200 to RM 800 and accepting a Property Use and Development Agreement in connection therewith (Petition of Helen Flager, C.F. 285414, Hearing Examiner No. X-77-251).
